# Privacy Policy

- We do **not collect or store** any personal information from users.  
- All QR and NFC scanning is done **locally on the device**.  
- The app does **not use any third-party analytics** or tracking services.  
- No scanned data is sent to any external servers.  
- The app does **not require login or account creation**.  
- Permissions are only used to access the **camera** (for QR) and **NFC hardware**, and are not misused.  
- We do **not share data with any third parties**. 
